1. AWS CDK (Cloud Development Kit):

AWS CDK is an open-source software development framework that enables you to define AWS resources using familiar programming languages such as TypeScript, Python, Java, or C#. With AWS CDK, you can create reusable constructs that represent your infrastructure components, making it easy to compose and share your infrastructure across different applications and environments.

